# Assets Other Non Financial Assets Plant And Equipment Accumulated Depreciation And Impairment Amount

## identifier
de8792

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of accumulated depreciation and impairment on items of plant and equipment, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.OtherNonFinancialAssets.PlantAndEquipmentAccumulatedDepreciationAndImpairment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.06
- period=instant
